I'm stuck, He'll find me,

812
01:03:19,171 --> 01:03:21,160
好 別說話了 別動
OK, stop talking. Don't move.

813
01:03:21,238 --> 01:03:23,898
他殺了兩個人      什麼
He killed two guys.        What?

814
01:03:23,972 --> 01:03:27,201
