He's got a knife, Eddie, I can't think my way out of a knife,

823
01:03:53,716 --> 01:03:55,807
聽我的話 30秒鐘後藥就會生效
Just listen to me, It'll come on in 30 seconds,

824
01:03:55,883 --> 01:03:57,782
然後你再思考要怎麼脫身 藥就有這個功效
And you'll think your way out, That's what it does,

825
01:04:21,259 --> 01:04:24,852
他越走越近了
He's getting closer,

826
01:04:27,494 --> 01:04:28,960
琳迪 我愛你
Lindy, I love you,

827
01:05:00,640 --> 01:05:02,572
嗨
Hey!

828
01:05:40,252 --> 01:05:41,844
