Hey, hey, hey, hey!

830
01:05:47,190 --> 01:05:49,747
啊!      爸爸!
Ah!        Daddy!

831
01:06:00,093 --> 01:06:01,683
艾迪 給
Eddie, Here,

832
01:06:02,794 --> 01:06:04,885
沒事了
It's gonna be OK,

833
