Well, you might have to live it without me,

854
01:07:52,613 --> 01:07:55,274
我會戒掉的 只是現在需要解決些事情
Look, I am gonna stop taking it, There's just some things I have to do

855
01:07:55,275 --> 01:07:58,872
確保我倆的安全 安排好一切 然後我就會戒
to keep us safe and that... To set us up and then I'm gonna get off it,

856
01:07:58,949 --> 01:08:00,576
我本來就是這麼打算的      艾迪
I mean, that's the plan,        Eddie...

857
01:08:00,649 --> 01:08:02,946
我真的都打算好了 我發誓
Look, I have a plan, I swear,

858
01:08:03,017 --> 01:08:04,812
我會戒的
I'm gonna get off it,

859
01:08:06,252 --> 01:08:07,582
好吧
OK,

860
01:08:09,553 --> 01:08:11,109
我希望你能做到
I hope you do,

861
01:08:43,297 --> 01:08:45,196
要找我嗎
Looking for me?

862
01:08:47,566 --> 01:08:49,220
你以為你能跑掉 是嗎 
You think you can run out on me, huh? 

863
01:08:49,700 --> 01:08:51,228
你以為我不知道你躲在哪裡
You think I don't know where you are?

864
01:08:51,300 --> 01:08:53,096
我認為我們之間的生意已經做完了
I was under the impression our business was settled,

865
01:08:53,168 --> 01:08:54,964
再給我些那種藥
I want some more of that stuff,

866
01:08:55,035 --> 01:08:58,002
不然我就當場崩了你 自己選
Or I shoot you right here, Take your pick,

867
01:08:58,070 --> 01:08:59,866
這傢伙是打發不走的
This guy was not going away.

868
01:08:59,937 --> 01:09:01,698
給他幾片藥能為我爭取到時間
A few pills would buy me some time.

869
01:09:01,770 --> 01:09:05,169
給 我們兩清了      走著瞧吧
There it is, We're done,        Oh, yeah, We'll see,

870
01:09:05,239 --> 01:09:07,831
直到我找到更...長久的解決辦法
Until I found a more... permanent solution.

871
01:09:08,507 --> 01:09:09,912
除非我真的身陷險境 
Unless you see a real threat, 

872
01:09:09,912 --> 01:09:12,374
我不希望能察覺到自己身邊有保鏢
I never want it known that I have any security,

873
01:09:12,442 --> 01:09:14,270
你們不需要為我開道 只需要跟著我
You'll never precede me, you'll always follow me,

874
01:09:14,271 --> 01:09:18,197
