Never more than 15 steps behind, And never stand too close together,

875
01:09:18,276 --> 01:09:20,971
我希望自己回頭的時候還能看見你倆之間有空隙
I want to able to look behind me if the opportunity presents itself,

876
01:09:22,411 --> 01:09:24,673
不要穿同樣顏色的西裝 這不是什麼黑客帝國
And don't wear the same color suit, This isn't The Matrix.

877
01:09:30,414 --> 01:09:32,574
你得明白 艾迪 我把你打發了
You have to know, Eddie, I wrote you off,

878
01:09:32,648 --> 01:09:34,308
我當時病了      你沒資格生病
I was sick,        You don't get sick,

879
01:09:34,382 --> 01:09:37,110
生意做到這份上 有口氣就得上 你還沒死呢
You're playing at this level, you get hit by a car, you don't even die,

880
01:09:37,183 --> 01:09:39,843
你說得完全正確      我知道我是對的
You're absolutely right,        I know I'm right,

881
01:09:39,917 --> 01:09:41,817
我都不知道我在和誰浪費時間
I mean, I didn't know who or what I was talking to,

882
01:09:41,886 --> 01:09:45,114
我當時燒到40度 卡爾 神志恍惚
A hundred and five, That's who you were talking to, Carl, Delirium,

883
01:09:45,186 --> 01:09:46,000
對
Mm-hm,

884
01:09:47,400 --> 01:09:49,560
我把修改過的預測發過來了
I sent over my revised projections,

885
01:09:49,560 --> 01:09:50,833
我沒讓你發什麼預測
I didn't ask for your projections,

886
01:09:50,833 --> 01:09:53,588
我明白 但只要你看過了的話...
I know, but I think if you take a look at them...

887
01:09:53,588 --> 01:09:55,617
我已經看過了 事實上
I already have, As a matter of fact...

888
01:09:57,188 --> 01:10:00,383
我已經根據你的預測炒掉了一些人
...I fired a few people over your projections,

889
01:10:00,456 --> 01:10:02,082
我很抱歉      不 你才沒有
I'm sorry,        No, you're not,

890
01:10:02,157 --> 01:10:04,988
你慶幸自己知道我的團隊沒留意的事
You're relieved that you know things my team missed,

891
01:10:05,057 --> 01:10:09,582
這一刻 一切簡直不可思議...
The minute, the instant that's no longer true...

892
01:10:12,494 --> 01:10:14,284
服用NZT兩個月後
Two months after I'd started NZT,

893
01:10:14,285 --> 01:10:17,287
我主持了商業史上最大的合併計劃
I was brokering the biggest merger in corporate history.

894
01:10:17,362 --> 01:10:19,654
諷刺的是 關鍵在於原油 
Ironically, it's gonna be crude, 

895
01:10:20,300 --> 01:10:21,798
原油是我們切入的最佳方位
Crude is gonna be where we're gonna hit them,

896
01:10:21,864 --> 01:10:24,489
這部分利潤高達百分之兩百
Which yields a prospective profit of 200 percent,

897
01:10:24,564 --> 01:10:26,428
這會讓每個人都喜出望外
That makes both of us very happy campers,

898
01:10:26,498 --> 01:10:28,897
我發現只要保持合理攝入量
I found that if I maintained an even dose,

899
01:10:28,966 --> 01:10:31,330
按時吃飯 不沾酒精
remembered to eat, drank no alcohol,

900
01:10:31,400 --> 01:10:33,798
頭腦空窗期就再沒發生過      你還好吧 艾迪
the blackouts didn't recur.        How you doing, Eddie?

901
01:10:34,768 --> 01:10:37,735
湯姆 衣服裡能加暗袋嗎
Tom, is it possible to construct an imperceptible compartment?

902
01:10:37,803 --> 01:10:39,269
在這件上面嗎
In this jacket?

903
01:10:39,336 --> 01:10:42,769
所有衣服上面      當然可以 先生
In all of them,        Certainly, sir,

904
01:10:42,837 --> 01:10:44,946
與其在這裡坐吃山空 
Safer though my stash now was, 

905
01:10:44,946 --> 01:10:46,966
不如先想辦法
I was not sitting around until it ran out.

906
01:10:47,039 --> 01:10:49,600
我能按同樣的配方製作出同樣的藥物嗎 
Can I combine these ingredients in the same exact quantity, 

907
01:10:49,600 --> 01:10:50,371
當然可以 不過
yes, but,

908
01:10:50,440 --> 01:10:55,237
它能否起到同樣的作用...不好說
the exact method of delivery to the brain... Darts at a dartboard,

909
01:10:55,308 --> 01:10:57,935
什麼意思      還需要臨床試驗 在人身上試驗
Meaning?        Clinical trials, guinea pig people,

910
01:10:58,010 --> 01:11:00,533
