before we even took notice,

939
01:12:49,782 --> 01:12:51,476
老天 他看上去不堪一擊
Jesus, he looks frail,

940
01:12:52,516 --> 01:12:54,881
可能是裝出來的      他還不到60歲
Could be an act,        He's not even 60,

941
01:12:57,218 --> 01:13:00,276
決定好了嗎 艾迪 你準備怎麼辦
So, have you decided, Eddie? What are you gonna do?

942
01:13:00,352 --> 01:13:03,444
併購結束之後? 我不知道
When this is over? I don't know,

943
01:13:03,520 --> 01:13:04,918
